BT - Bit Test:
| Opcode             | Instruction   | Op/En| 64-bit Mode| Compat/Leg Mode| Description                   
| 0F A3 /r           | BT r/m16, r16 | MR   | Valid      | Valid          | Store selected bit in CF flag.
