PUSHF/PUSHFD - Push EFLAGS Register onto the Stack:
| Opcode*| Instruction| Op/En| 64-Bit Mode| Compat/Leg Mode| Description                  
| 9C     | PUSHF      | NP   | Valid      | Valid          | Push lower 16 bits of EFLAGS.
